===星夜的翻版===
《群山中的橄榄树》現藏于[[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]。梵高曾在給他弟弟的信中說：“我畫了一幅風景畫，這也是對星空的一次再發現”。相對于描繪夜晚的《[[星夜|星夜]]》，這幅畫描繪的則是橄欖樹和白天的天空。他作畫的目的是反抗“某些畫家照片一樣完美”的作品。<ref name="MOMA">{{cite web |url=http://www.moma.org/collection/object.php?object_id=80013 |title=Olive Trees, June–July 1889 |author= |year=2010 |work=Painting and Sculpture, Vincent van Gogh |publisher=Museum of Modern Art |accessdate=March 25, 2011 |postscript=The text on the page is referenced to The Museum of Modern Art, MoMA Highlights, New York: The Museum of Modern Art, revised 2004, originally published 1999, p. 34 |archive-date=2015-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131135619/http://www.moma.org/collection/object.php?object_id=80013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

